{"tid":2040070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"手足，生於亂世，一時退卻並不可恥","createTime":"2020-05-28T10:47:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T23:41:53.000Z","uid":281401,"like":74,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0268653971f8f34ff529d6933cdf05e78eb109ab","tid":2040070,"uid":281401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:47:28.000Z","msg":"啱啱一位天水圍手足係藍屍街站遇襲，無人救援，<br />\n最後根據天水連線既情報，該名手足確認被捕。<br />\n<br />\n我知道手足有時難免怒火中燒，難免會衝動。<br />\n我知道道理係企我地嗰邊。<br />\n<br />\n但係，形勢唔係企係我嗰邊。<br />\n當你勢孤力弱，你第一樣嘢要緊記既係，保護自己。<br />\n香港要贏，香港人就要生存落嚟，<br />\n唔好因為一時意氣，就誤墮陷阱。<br />\n<br />\n係呢個時代，一時退卻並不可恥。<br />\n因為藍屍打你斬你，係唔會有任何後果；<br />\n因為報警，班狗嚟到，只會拉你，唔會主持公道。<br />\n呢個，係呢個亂世既常態。<br />\n<br />\n我之前睇<strong>《Jojo Rabbit》</strong>發現有段對白，係好啱我地。<br />\n係戲入面，Scarlett Johansson扮演一名德國婦人（Rosie），佢收留咗一名猶太女仔，<br />\n呢個係佢地既對話：<br />\n<br />\nELSA:<br />\n<strong>They&rsquo;ve been winning so far. </strong>　（佢地一路贏緊。）<br />\n<br />\nROSIE:<br />\n<em>They&rsquo;ll never win. That is the power you<br />\nhave - as long as there is someone alive<br />\nsomewhere then they lose. They didn&rsquo;t get<br />\nyou yesterday, or today. Make tomorrow<br />\nthe same.</em><br />\n<br />\n（佢地永遠都唔會贏。只要一日，你地有人係某處倖存落黎，<br />\n佢地就會輸。佢地尋日捉你唔到，今日都捉你唔到，聽日都要一樣。）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8MYTDKR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8MYTDKR.jpg&h=82b01f0f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"83e93b69a52ecefef127caac6a8c51aaedb68339","tid":2040070,"uid":19817,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:48:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2039830/page/1#preview\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2039830/page/1#preview</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>攬炒要有覺悟</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"28779e5e975d5d6759cc7159b3b9d674fd677f0c","tid":2040070,"uid":174120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T